title: "Why Tesla Stock Is Accelerating Today"
text: "Morgan Stanley upgraded Tesla on the potential of its Dojo supercomputer. Analyst Adam Jonas sees Dojo generating earnings similar to what Amazon has done with its AWS business."

title: "Dojo Could Boost Tesla Value by $500B: Morgan Stanley"
text: "Tesla Inc.'s Dojo supercomputer may add as much as $500 billion to the company's market value through faster adoption of robotaxis and network services
source_name: according to Morgan Stanley. Bloomberg's Ed Ludlow has more on the call by Adam Jonas."

title: "iPhone 15 isn't going to reignite Apple's stock
date: DA Davidson managing director and senior research analyst
topics: joins 'Squawk on the Street' to discuss Apple's 'neutral' price target and potential risks to the stock."
